Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第6話 真假!?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可以幫妳洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:34.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:36.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為是我穿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,自己洗很正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:39.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那首先就從假髮開始洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把柔軟劑放進冷水或溫水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把用梳子梳順的假髮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,輕輕搓洗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:55.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像 像這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:56.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:00:59.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搓揉過度的話會傷到假髮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:04.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接著把水換掉再搓洗一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用毛巾包著擦乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後再陰乾就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 超簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還以為更難…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為會沾上汗漬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:17.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服裝也用手洗吧…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,假髮洗太久也不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然被那種事嚇到跌倒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:38.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼叫那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那可是女用的貼身衣物喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是絲襪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:43.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又沒有什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小新也是高中男生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有一兩件很正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我回來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 兩個禮拜都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新菜!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海夢 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喊得那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:28.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺我還以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們沒有做什麼虧心事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看了這個之後我也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但你做得滿不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:39.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做得很出色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但還有很多不足的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 像是這裡還有這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,差點就因為以往的習慣用膠水黏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和娃娃的做法不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為都是曲線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-這是怎麼回事 -不知道要怎樣才能做出這個形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一開始的時候不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有這裡 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-不妙 -原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為平時都是直線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:14.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真的喜歡上五条同學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,騙…騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜歡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且還很是喜歡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:17.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜番?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之和爺爺在一起就開啟了話匣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜番五条同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:36.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學 妳餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真想死!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不介意的話在我們家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:52.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學也很會做料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 沒那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:07.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我家雙親都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只好自己來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真假 那和我一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:18.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們家媽媽以前因為生病過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只有我和爸爸兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,考上高中之後 爸爸也被調職
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:23.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,獨自在外地工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(抱歉 海夢)\N獨自在外地工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(抱歉 海夢)\N我現在就像一個人生活那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,南瓜也好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-好甜 -那還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:33.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然基本都是買便利商店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但沒有打工的日子我還滿常煮飯的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是納豆冷凍炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(油膩膩…黏答答…)\N冷凍炸雞佐小香腸飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(油膩膩…黏答答…)\N有一陣子因為迷上了就一直吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我姑且還是會做料理的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身體有哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我每天都有喝牛奶還有吃優格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海夢 如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之後都在我們家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以吧 新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就這麼做吧 喜多川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學 謝謝你送我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:25.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拖到這麼晚 我才要向妳道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:28.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,晚餐非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和爺爺聊天也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的完全搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明只是普通的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼會沒來由的緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們沒有做什麼虧心事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虧心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像做了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也好像有說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正想說要出門 就下得這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生一個人到我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是新菜的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小姐 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:46.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,閃耀著璀璨色彩的重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:52.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不會忘記的 沒錯 就是這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在水平線的遙遠彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:07.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,流露的嘆息隨著波浪消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你找出了我隱藏的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:18.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,並牽起我的手向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:24.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,滿面笑容的你映入了眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:29.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,波浪濺起時的兩個身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,響起的腳步聲邁向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:41.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不斷追逐著陽光下赤腳的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:46.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敞開心胸潑起了水花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爛漫搖曳的水面染上璀璨色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:57.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,初次相遇了這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:02.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真摯地注視著夢想的美麗雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:07.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想在你身旁相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Be myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有你朋友來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為她都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在正在讓她泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等她出來 拿點喝的給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:39.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底讓誰進了家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學說了今天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也沒有喜多川同學以外的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該不會!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:52.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,詐欺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:54.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新類型的小偷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺被騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爺爺我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼這個娃娃沒有長頭髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,頭和頭髮是分別製作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順序是先把臉畫好才裝上頭髮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才光溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:44.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,光溜溜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問今天有何貴幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服 服裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是你做的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是來參觀娃娃製作的客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為是一個人來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以爺爺才以為是我的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的 有在製作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麻煩告訴我姓名和學校名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾紗壽葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,櫻之宮女子高中二年級喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原 原來年紀比我大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是五条新菜 高中一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 如果是服裝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬上就可以參觀喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然只有一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在就想看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請盡情參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:10.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有人對娃娃感興趣果然很讓人開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那些娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,頭的話在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是分別進行製作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之後才合而為一的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有點獵奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這件和服用了施華洛世奇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個用了蕾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和以前的差很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:38.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在也順應時代做了這種類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可以靠近點看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:44.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不會碰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是很重要的商品對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感謝妳的顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳看得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是很受歡迎的娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,美得讓人目不轉睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也覺得很美麗 非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有這邊的娃娃也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們在看女兒節娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因…因為我們是賣女兒節娃娃的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說的是COSPLAY的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個是你做的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是來訂製COSPLAY服裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就 就算妳說要訂製
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也沒有在賣COSPLAY服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在浴室…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看到我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,偷窺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 你那是偷窺喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:53.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要我報警的話 你就會被逮捕喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明都沒有被別人看過的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不想要我報警的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幫朱朱我做服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:22.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我超喜歡朱朱小姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學說過喜歡的那個COSER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起來滿年幼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問她幾歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該是國中生之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問…朱朱小姐為什麼在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我家在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:00.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我看到了那個 叫海夢的女生她COS的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那之後她發推說要去COSPLAY活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為想要靠近看看服裝就去了活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,胸口處好像快破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這是依照喜多川同學的尺寸做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後就發現是你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就跟蹤了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(絕對不要這麼做)\N這個行動力!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(打工結束了! 現在就過去五条同學家)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:33.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真假…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這位是乾紗壽葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別說出本名啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是有COS名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人叫做紗壽葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超級可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我叫喜多川海夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真的真的超喜歡朱朱大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是妳的大粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下 太靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本人真的也是美少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,皮膚真不是一般的光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,頭髮好細
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說是因為叫紗壽葉才取名朱朱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又 又不是我取的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾同學好像看過喜多川同學的照片喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才會到我家來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,神COSER看過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人知道我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只 只是剛好看到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後妳也有跟隨我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超不妙 好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就說妳靠太近了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別誤會了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不是對妳感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是對五条新菜製作的服裝有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,眼睛好大 超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽我說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:39.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望你能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:43.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幫我做二階堂紫苑的黑百合服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小紫苑?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小紫苑不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像在之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,花公主烈的小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然是給小女生看的動畫 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我對動畫不是很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,公主百合!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二階堂紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是在花公主烈中出場的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和主角米萊一起變成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:09.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,魔法少女花公主和敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會讓你無法再次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在高傲的百合前站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,魔法少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,公主百合!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:20.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一直都在和姊姊戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道了最喜歡的姊姊音苑是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的體內是空無一物的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,紫苑 妳也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幸福是不會永遠持續下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虛偽的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人們輕蔑的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳真正想守護的是那種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要 住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳其實是想要摧毀掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這 這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,黑百合的誕生!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後想把一切事物都染色對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和妳的心一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,染上深淵的漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(二階堂姊妹在播出當時)\N(以小學女生和成年男性為中心)\N(獲得廣大的人氣)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音苑姊姊也是因為失戀的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,花寶石被汙染成為了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她也很可憐呢\N意外的有好好看過原作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯呢\N意外的有好好看過原作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:36.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯呢\N還以為她是只覺得"服裝很可愛"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也超喜歡音苑姊姊的\N還以為她是只覺得"服裝很可愛"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也超喜歡音苑姊姊的\N對原作和角色都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一般來說不管是誰經歷那種失戀\N對原作和角色都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一般來說不管是誰經歷那種失戀\N就隨便COS的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都會被汙染的\N就隨便COS的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:46.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音苑姊姊經歷了很慘痛的失戀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:51.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大致上就是兩個青梅竹馬的 男性朋友交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然設定上沒有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但只要有看就能從氛圍察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要看了就能察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"烈!!"的人際關係滿複雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米萊和紫苑都超喜歡朔夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把朔夜夾在中間吵得不可開交
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是朔夜已經和颯馬哥哥交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來就是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且颯馬哥哥還被音苑姊姊單戀著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,給小女生看的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,紫苑雖然是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但有著不幸的童年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也沒得到應有的回報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過不管她再怎麼艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都會充滿自信露出不服輸笑容的紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是我最喜歡的魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我也不想妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,黑百合的服裝設計
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:35.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很難用現成的服裝調整
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:39.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你能幫我製作 適合我的尺寸的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,COS黑百合的朱朱大人太不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超想看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:48.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同學很喜歡小紫苑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,包包上面也掛了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼喜歡的話也自己出就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 我是不會出的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:55.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我滿高的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和小紫苑纖細嬌小的感覺差很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然想說"喜歡就出不用在意那種事"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也完全說得過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但以我自己來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正因為喜歡才不想去破壞形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:08.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大概那種感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果要COS的話就要盡可能地貼近形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是像這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有如果是"烈!!"的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想要COS音苑姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是我最喜歡的那種COSER類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對這孩子明明什麼也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就擅自以為她沒有認真的在COS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但她完全就不是那種討人厭的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不擠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原諒偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原諒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:51.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,制服應該也乾了 我去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能告訴我聯絡方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我把黑百合的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和我的尺寸表傳給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要誤會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是製作服裝的聯絡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誤會什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們在交往對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:13.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有我 我沒有和人交往過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一隻交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩隻交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-是我誤會了呢 -三隻交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四隻交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同學現在沒有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:34.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-真的假的 有這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然是個討人厭的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了 朱朱大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:44.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我剛剛不是說了如果是"烈!!"的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想COS音苑姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:56.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我來COS音苑姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能和我一起出"烈!!"嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:00.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還沒說完就被拒絕了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不經意地發現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定是陷入了戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為命運的作弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:34.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對那一句話怦然心動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:40.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不能再更期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在兩人追尋著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:50.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一心一意純潔的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:53.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,漸漸動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:57.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好 不小心就對你一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太喜歡你了 該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,坦率面對自己內心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以啊 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:15.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在身旁看著含苞待放的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NANANA NANANA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:35.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第7話)\N(和喜番的人在家約會太不妙了)